                            <comment id="13441496" author="jbellis" created="Fri, 24 Aug 2012 20:58:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Brandon says, &quot;Something is wrong w/ the upgrade of the system KS, not gossip.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13457889" author="xedin" created="Tue, 18 Sep 2012 15:35:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Actually it&apos;s a problem with Gossiper &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13457943" author="brandon.williams" created="Tue, 18 Sep 2012 16:47:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Can you explain what happened here?  I&apos;m confused by the version 11 change, given that trunk is version 12.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13458046" author="xedin" created="Tue, 18 Sep 2012 18:48:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sure, GossipDigestAckSerializer always expects boolean on deserialization, that would only changed in 1.2 which doesn&apos;t write that boolean.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13458242" author="brandon.williams" created="Tue, 18 Sep 2012 22:19:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I see, thanks. +1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13458249" author="xedin" created="Tue, 18 Sep 2012 22:25:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
